eval

public void eval(ec.EvolutionState state,
                 int thread,
                 ec.gp.GPData input,
                 ec.gp.ADFStack stack,
                 ec.gp.GPIndividual individual,
                 ec.Problem problem)
Try to evaluate the response. The method call for the response is identified if it has not already been. Once the method call is identified, the argument types are identified and stored. Next, the children are evaluated. The values received by the children are passed as arguments to the method call. The problem is *always* the object being used to invoke the method upon.
